            <ul type="disc">
                <li>The animated figure below gives a virtual experience of      measuring selective heights. These are normally measured by anthropometric      board and anthropometric rod set also as presented in the procedure      section. This hands on trial provides a feel of measuring the dimensions.</li>
                <li>Click the left hand side up/down arrow button to move      figure.</li>
                <li>.Users are expected to get the feel of the measuring      process through this animated experiment and are advised to measure in      real life practical situations using anthropometric rod sets and      anthropometric boards. Moreover, the users may select their own specific      landmarks as required.</li>
